  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK332">
<l>kūttāṭ ṭavaikkuḻāt taṟṟē peruñcelvam</l>
<l>pōkku matuviḷin taṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The acquisition of wealth is like the gathering together of an assembly for a theatre its expenditure is like the breaking up of that assembly.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
